OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy
OL,6,Fperiods with showers dying out to
OL,7,Fstart the evening, soon becoming
OL,8,Fgenerally dry with clear spells and
OL,9,Fthe wind easing. Cloud thickening
OL,10,Fovernight however, with rain arriving
OL,11,Fbefore dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FCloudy and damp start. Rain
OL,14,Fpossibly heavy first thing in the
OL,15,Fmorning, but mostly becoming confined
OL,16,Fto western parts in the afternoon.
OL,17,FBrighter spells developing later in
OL,18,Fthe east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
