OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry and
OL,6,Fwarmer during this period. Friday,
OL,7,Fwarm or very warm with hazy sunshine.
OL,8,FSaturday remaining warm with sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Mostly sunny and remaining
OL,10,Fwarm on Sunday.
